## Phase 0: Existing Analysis Check

Check if prior interview analyses exist for this project.

```bash
{{SLUG_EVAL}}
mkdir -p "${GSTACK_HOME:-$HOME/.gstack}/interviews"
echo "=== EXISTING ANALYSES ==="
ls -1t "${GSTACK_HOME:-$HOME/.gstack}/interviews/"*.md 2>/dev/null | head -20 || echo "No analyses found."
