## Phase 6: Review & Iterate

Present the top 3 findings and use AskUserQuestion:

> Your interview analysis is ready. Here's what jumped out:
>
> 1. **{Top pain}** — {one-line summary with evidence count}
> 2. **{Second pain}** — {one-line summary}
> 3. **{Top recommendation}** — {one-line summary}
>
> What would you like to do?
> - A) Challenge these findings — I think you're missing something
> - B) Go deeper on a specific pain or segment
> - C) Add more interviews to the analysis
> - D) It's solid — what's next?

If A: Ask what they think is missing. Re-read transcripts with that lens.
If B: Deep dive on the requested area.
If C: Return to Phase 1 for additional transcripts, then merge.
If D: Proceed to next-skill recommendations.

